    <string name="alert_mars_weather_message">Ever wondered what the weather is like on Mars? Never forget to bring a jacket out on your leisurely trip up Olympus Mons again thanks to this handy activity! The activity provides weather information from the most recent data gathered by the Curiosity Rover, using the MAAS 2 Rest API.</string>
